relation: Darrow5 - #54 Something lurks in the waters, ready to strike. With a terrifying screech, it emerges and appears. The Kraken, terror of the sea, appears!
Darrow5 - #53 Sailing further on brings signs of a storm, though something is off. Could this be what the captain wanted to avoid?
Darrow5 - #52 Sailing along, the boat passes by a few interesting looking islands. If only it were possible to stop and check them out. Curse you, interesting-looking-but-non-explorable islands!

Darrow5 - #51 Although Reggie's letter is full of lies and almost entirely fictional, the captain does have a habit of getting sea sick. Still, he pushes forward with his job and loves every minute of it. What a trooper.
Darrow5 - #50 With a boat secured, the four heroes sail off towards their next adventure.
